# Lucide Icon Standard

- Use `lucide-react` for all icons in this project.
- Do not add new inline `<svg>` icons in components unless there is no Lucide equivalent.
- Do not introduce other icon libraries (for example `react-icons`, `@heroicons/react`, or custom icon packs).
- Prefer importing only the icons you need, for example `import { Trash2 } from "lucide-react"`.
- Keep decorative icons `aria-hidden="true"` and pair action icons with readable labels (`sr-only` text) when needed.
